  "original_title": "Sri Lanka\u2019s state-run Litro reduces cooking gas prices",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka\u2019s state-run Litro reduces cooking gas prices",
      "author": "Dulya de Silva",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka\u2019s state owned Litro Gas has reduced domestic gas cylinder prices for the second consecutive month under a newly implemented pricing formula.",
        "Accordingly, the price of a 12.5kg gas cylinder will be reduced by 133 rupees to 4,551 rupees, Litro said in a statement on Monday Sep 05.",
        "The price of a 5kg cylinder has been reduced by 45 rupees down to 1,827 rupees and the price of a 2.3kg cylinder has been reduced by 21 rupees down to 848 rupees.",
        "This is the second slashing of prices since the price formula was implemented in July. (Colombo/Sep05/2022)"
      ],
